ğŸ”¹ 5. Sampling & Quantization (Very Detailed)

These are two steps in converting a continuous image â†’ digital image.

5.1 Sampling

Sampling = selecting pixel positions.

Increasing sampling â†’ high resolution

Decreasing sampling â†’ blocky, pixelated image

